This file is used for building Rinux
NOT for importing your own projects into Rinux
All commands are allowed


If you are getting the error 'Please use the enderpearl build system' try running
'enderpearl tryfix', fixed the issue 99% of the time
#TRYFIX(
echo '#![allow(dead_code)]pub(crate) const QUIET_BOOT: bool = {};'  > ./rinux/src/conf/mod.rs
cargo build --offline
cargo check
)



Building for release
#RELEASE(
cargo build --release
cargo bootimage --release
)